<h3 id="serial-port-drivers-for-windows">Serial port drivers for Windows</h3>

<p>The serial port drivers are necessary if using an Auto Flat <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">v1.3</code> board or older. If your board has a mini-USB port (not a micro-USB), then it needs the serial drivers.</p>

